{"tid":1775910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人幾時先肯升級","createTime":"2019-12-09T07:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T08:14:13.000Z","uid":189146,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"346dfa71f1e9dc262e2c4b4a61257db5276b12a7","tid":1775910,"uid":189146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"今日三罷<br />\n5點未到話出門口 早餐都未食幫你被罷工<br />\n出到嚟人都冇幾個 當你朝早醒唔到啦<br />\n等下晝幫人早放 你同我講去和你lunch???<br />\n三罷變和你lunch 我都唔知講咩好<br />\n叫人幫手又話我係鬼<br />\n叫人下次唔係罷嘅唔好叫人6點出去 又話我係分化撚<br />\n個撚個得把口 得啦 你地慢慢玩啦 等到2047先罷啦<br />\n人少又搞到有手足比狗咬<br />\n<br />\n和理非成日叫勇武抖下先<br />\n128都做左成日和理非啦<br />\n咁和理非幾時先可以升級<br />\n根本三罷呢樣野可以唔洗靠勇武<br />\n我好撚攰 好撚灰心 但下次都仲係會好撚天真咁出左去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人報仇</span> 你唔出嚟又點報仇"},{"pid":"8a499c0254289c85645405efd370c86181cbeaf2","tid":1775910,"uid":261505,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:12:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老味又分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n與其屌人唔做咩唔做咩 不如做好自己同身邊人先"},{"pid":"58c641030d4a79255af4393464d45402668b5d77","tid":1775910,"uid":57738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"85802d951285bd8d469eec93f265aac53787d739","tid":1775910,"uid":323018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cee03491ed86ef721f62fa5da7dbda0eb61f51","tid":1775910,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"罷工咁易咩<br />\n話罷就罷？"},{"pid":"45d43f7202290a93936efd23dc55b0079d1bdfd5","tid":1775910,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"［改抗爭模式］想真罷工成功既請入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1775920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1775920</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8f32b1fa6ba306093c92be648e45ad219ba3787e","tid":177591